Articles.Content: So i wanna to know if there is any Delta IV mods for 1.0

When it this is properly updated for 1.0, this is a pretty good bet.

http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/64993-0-90-Chaka-Monkey-Exploration-Odyssey-0-27-1-EFT-1-Commemorative-Edition

You can make a decent Delta IV 5.2 from this pack.

You can get a stock-tuned variant of the Delta IV's RS-68 engine in this pack: http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/117766-1-0-Cryogenic-Engines-Pack-%28high-Isp-chemical-rockets!%29

Includes the ability to load liquid hydrogen into regular tanks (or LF only for the LV-N).
